  "text": "To estimate total phosphorus (TP) efflux from mussels, we multiplied areal mussel TDP excretion rates by an empirically derived mussel TDP : TP efflux ratio of 1 : 1.67 [CITATION_1] . TP fluxes from mussels were 10 6 3, 33 6 11, and 11 6 4 mg P m 22 d 21 on 21 August, 1 September, and 10 September, respectively. Daily mussel TP fluxes were estimated by linear interpolation and summed to give a total flux of 446 6 148 mg P m 22 , or 21 6 7 mg P m 22 d 21 (Fig. 4f, gray fill) . Summed PP fluxes from the water column were 445 6 22 mg P m 22 , or 21 6 1 mg P m 22 d 21 (Fig. 4f , black fill).",
